A new solo Wolverine adventure begins! Logan is thrown into a wild battle filled with dragons, kung fu masters and a talking gorilla! By Jason Aaron and Ron Garney!

Also: Deadpool is being hunted by Captain America, and his sinister counterpart Evil Deadpool is still on the loose! Lots more madness from Daniel Way and Salva Espin!

Featuring material first published in Wolverine #17-18 and Deadpool #47-48.

The final Fear Itself chapter! The possessed Hulk smashes his way through the Vampire Nation – is this the end of Dracula?! By Victor Gischler and Ryan Stegman!

Also: The Red Hulk battles Omegex, the unstoppable alien assassin! More action from Jeff Parker and Gabriel Hardman!

Plus: Skaar battles the forces of the mysterious Designer in the Savage Land! By Rob Williams and Brian Ching!

Collects:

  • Fear Itself: Hulk vs Dracula #3
  • Skaar: King of the Savage Land #3
  • Hulk #39.

Norman Osborn is back, and he wants the Avengers dead! Hero battles hero as Osborn springs a lethal trap, and a long-lost Avenger returns! By Brian Michael Bendis, Daniel Acuna and Renato Guedes!

Featuring material first published in Avengers #19-21 and New Avengers #19.
